<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 12:46:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>币安在崩溃批评后收紧做市规则</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/binance-tightens-market-making-rules-in-wake-of-crash-criticism</link><description>全球最大的加密货币交易所币安 (Binance) 在 10 月份市场崩溃期间对数字资产市场做法提出批评后，正在收紧对该平台上的代币发行者和流动性提供者的规则。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iBEjkjyVrqRk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 18:38:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/binance-tightens-market-making-rules-in-wake-of-crash-criticism</guid></item><item><title>英国因存在干扰风险而禁止政治加密货币捐赠</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/uk-should-ban-crypto-donations-to-political-parties-review-says</link><description>英国政府宣布暂停以加密货币进行政治捐赠，并对海外选民的礼物设置上限，部长们试图遏制外国金融干预英国政治的风险。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/impmHx8XE9.c/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 12:39:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/uk-should-ban-crypto-donations-to-political-parties-review-says</guid></item><item><title>随着市场崩盘动摇信心，币安对加密货币的控制放松</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/binance-s-grip-on-crypto-loosens-as-market-crash-rattles-faith</link><description>币安控股有限公司曾经对加密货币交易的控制程度在传统市场中是不可想象的。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iH6LpTpV0E5A/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 13:27:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/binance-s-grip-on-crypto-loosens-as-market-crash-rattles-faith</guid></item><item><title>琼斯表示，澳大利亚央行将数字代币的关注重点从“如果”转向“如何”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/rba-shifting-focus-on-digital-tokens-from-if-to-how-jones-says</link><description>澳大利亚央行助理行长布拉德·琼斯表示，澳大利亚央行已将重点从批发数字代币是否会在金融体系中发挥作用转向如何实施，因为它希望在试点项目后释放效率收益。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igoogbybOI3s/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 02:40:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/rba-shifting-focus-on-digital-tokens-from-if-to-how-jones-says</guid></item><item><title>加密货币交易者正在转变为大型跨资产追逐者</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-24/crypto-perps-platforms-are-increasingly-used-for-trading-tradfi-assets</link><description>Hyperliquid、Ostium 等网站发现传统资产永续资产占据了更大的交易量份额&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iViar1s5soj4/v9/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-24/crypto-perps-platforms-are-increasingly-used-for-trading-tradfi-assets</guid></item><item><title>加密巨头寻求审计，Tether 里程碑式的筹款活动被搁置</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-24/tether-s-landmark-fundraise-on-hold-as-crypto-giant-seeks-audit</link><description>Tether Holdings SA 筹集高达 200 亿美元的计划已暂停，这家稳定币巨头正在等待其首次全面财务审计的结果，此举可能会重启数字资产时代最受期待的筹款活动之一。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iscYrrRPyyGc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 19:29:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-24/tether-s-landmark-fundraise-on-hold-as-crypto-giant-seeks-audit</guid></item><item><title>比特币的制度转变推动 Bernstein 买入 15 万美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-24/bitcoin-s-institutional-shift-drives-bernstein-s-150-000-call</link><description>Bernstein 表示，比特币很可能已经触底，到 2026 年底可能会升至 15 万美元，该公司认为，加密货币正在通过机构所有权和融资的稳步转变而被重塑。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iEyVmo9BBf4o/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 16:09:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-24/bitcoin-s-institutional-shift-drives-bernstein-s-150-000-call</guid></item></channel></rss>